description: Try our easy to follow Thai-Flavoured Sausage Rolls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: ThaiFlavoured Sausage Rolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Place 1 sheet of filo pastry onto a flat surface. Spray with olive oil. Fold in half, so short edges meet.
Place half of the reserved turkey mixture at one end, leaving a 6cm border on each side. Fold sides over filling and roll up to form a sausage shape. Place onto a baking tray lined with baking paper.

Repeat with a second filo sheet and remaining turkey mixture. Spray with oil and sprinkle with sesame seeds. Bake for 1015 minutes or until pastry is golden and crisp. Cool. Place into an airtight container with a small tub of sweet chilli sauce.
